## Corrections from the Initial (Rejected) Phase 4 Draft

The first Phase 4 draft contained factual errors that this plan corrects:
- ~~"rate_limit decorator is a no-op"~~ — it is enabled and enforced by default (`aitbc/rate_limiting.py:24`).
- ~~"move auth/dependencies.py and security_matrix.py into coordinator-api"~~ — they already live there; the real duplication was the JWT *library* (PyJWT vs python-jose), not those files.
- ~~"health endpoint rate=50, will be throttled"~~ — it's `rate=1000, per=60` (`routers/health.py:15`).
- ~~"agent_stream.py has 5 E501 errors"~~ — ruff now reports clean (fixed in C1).
- File counts corrected: agent-coordinator 61 (not 48), coordinator-api 485 (not 508), contexts 34 (not 35).
